song_lyrics: Ab kahā pūchhu purānī panḍit, chhed bhayorī antar chhatiyāse... °ṭek
Mohā moh mile nij prītam, ko patiyār kare patiyāse... Man° 1
Swargādik sukh sapane na chāhu, chāh nahi chāru gatiyāse... Man° 2
Dās Mukund vās behadme, po’ch nahi prākṛut matiyāse... Man° 3
title: Man mānyo Mohan batiyāse
